operation even in transient periods (presence of clouds). Also, from a theoretical annual study for the solar {MED} system, it was found that the annual solar fraction ranges from 30.7\% to 42.4\%, which leads to an annual distillate production between 6701m3 and 11,314m3, respectively.},
