mics of this method is described. Greenhouses are important in dry regions which have intensive solar radiation and no usable water resources. The combination of solar-driven H/D method and solar stills with greenhouses to supply the necessary humidity to the greenhouse plants gives a good solution to produce simultaneously fresh water and crops in dessert lands. A short description of this combination and figures of installations is presented.},
